## 📁 After Installation — What Gets Created

```
DocuGuard/
├── venv/                ← Virtual environment (if you created one)
├── data/
│   └── registry.json   ← Auto-created when first document is registered
└── ...
```

The `data/` folder stores only cryptographic hashes — never document contents.

